item.title: my project site is fancy
item.description: much more so than this wordpress stuff…. haha! So, I guess I consider this blog (factorq.net) my “personal blog” of any variety of opinionation and open source and other ramblings. My other website, jrob.co.cc (now jrobb.org), I suppose is my site dedicated to projects I work on and develop. At work, I have several programs that I have developed, mostly all under the umbrella of one large program–all written in VB6, unfortunately.
